{
  "stem": "24615.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We finished the food and a big bread, both of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the lady crossed herself as we were eating, as we were finishing with food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we walked out, we were just walking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- afraid-- we weren't afraid if the Ukrainian will run after us, what happen or nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we walked back, you know, to another farm, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was before they killed the [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a miracle too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was so many miracles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I was staying with this [NON-ENGLISH], and-- and they were threatening me, should give me over to the Germans and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were just, the scale was weighing, you know, on it, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how I came to this country and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never dreamed about America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never dreamed like to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never even dreamed I would be alive, after-- I'll survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never dreamed the Russians will come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought that's all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the end, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is there anything else you would like to add or anything else you would like to say to anybody who might be watching this or to your family or to anyone about the Holocaust and what it's meant to you?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hope it never happens again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You think it can happen?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hope it never, never happens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another thing is, I'm glad our children are born in this country, you [CRYING] Because I-- I don't trust Poland, I don't trust Russia or Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't trust anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't even trust here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I don't know what ever can happen here, just because we live like this, because I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If it wouldn't be for my wife, I wouldn't even buy the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
